OL,4,CHanson 'paralysed with fear during
OL,5,Cviolence'
OL,7,FThe wife of television auctioneer
OL,8,FCharles Hanson was "paralysed with
OL,9,Ffear" when her husband was violent
OL,10,Ftowards her while she was pregnant, a
OL,11,Fcourt has heard.
OL,13,FRebecca Hanson told Derby Crown Court
OL,14,Fon Tuesday that on another occasion
OL,15,Fher husband, who is accused of hurting
OL,16,Fand leaving marks on her during 10
OL,17,Fyears of violence, threatened to burn
OL,18,Fher with embers from a fire.
