OL,4,CHanson 'paralysed with fear during
OL,5,Cviolence'
OL,7,FThe 46-year-old television
OL,8,Fpersonality, of Ashbourne Road in
OL,9,FMackworth, Derby, is charged with
OL,10,Fcontrolling or coercive behaviour,
OL,11,Fassault occasioning actual bodily
OL,12,Fharm, and assault by beating, which he
OL,13,Fhas denied.
OL,15,FHis wife told the jury of seven women
OL,16,Fand five men that their marriage was
OL,17,F"generally OK" at the beginning before
OL,18,Fthe violence "escalated".
