OL,7,FMrs Hanson said she was "petrified"
OL,8,Fwhen the first incident happened in
OL,9,F2012, around two years after they
OL,10,Fmarried, when her husband "went for"
OL,11,Fher while she was five or six months
OL,12,Fpregnant with a baby the couple later
OL,13,Flost.
OL,15,FShe told the court: "Charles had
OL,16,Fobviously had an operation for
OL,17,Ftesticular cancer and I was pregnant.
OL,18,FIt's common that when Charles is ill
OL,19,Fhe gets extra irritable and angry."
