OL,7,F"He just ran towards where I was stood
OL,8,Fin the door frame. I turned around to
OL,9,Fprotect my stomach and my baby. He got
OL,10,Fme round the throat.
OL,12,F"He's behind me with his arm around my
OL,13,Fthroat, tight, with my head back.
OL,15,F"It felt like a very long time...I
OL,16,Fthink realistically probably about
OL,17,Ffour, five seconds, but it felt like
OL,18,Fminutes. I froze. I was absolutely
OL,19,Fpetrified and in shock.
