OL,7,F"I completely froze, I was paralysed
OL,8,Fwith fear. I could not believe he was
OL,9,Fdoing it. I think he was shocked at
OL,10,Fwhat he had done, I could not believe
OL,11,Fwhat he had done especially because I
OL,12,Fwas pregnant."
OL,14,FSasha Wass KC, defending, said to Mrs
OL,15,FHanson: "Charles never put you in a
OL,16,Fheadlock. What happened was this ` he
OL,17,Fand you were having words.
OL,19,F"He said 'come on love' and he hugged
OL,20,Fyou tightly around the shoulder,
OL,21,Fnowhere near your neck."
